#

Balsamic Fig-Glazed Beef Tenderloin

40 min
$25
350 kcal
Difficulty: 25%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh Protein

Cuisine:

AmericanMediterranean

Course:

Main CourseDinner

Tags:

EasyQuickSavoryMain Course

Description

A succulent beef tenderloin glazed with a sweet and tangy balsamic fig sauce, perfect for an easy yet impressive meal.

Ingredients

  • beef tenderloin: 1.5 lbs
  • balsamic vinegar: 1/2 cup
  • fig jam: 1/4 cup
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • fresh rosemary: 1 tablespoon, chopped (optional)
